02:12.666 --> 02:14.166
You know, they sell
those in stores.

02:14.168 --> 02:15.734
Yeah, but have you seen
how much they cost?

02:15.736 --> 02:18.804
It's outrageous.
Yours are much more affordable.

02:18.806 --> 02:21.840
Hey, what do you say
you and I go see the
roller derby tonight?

02:21.842 --> 02:24.376
