elbowing each other
into your lap?

02:35.923 --> 02:38.824
I don't know,
teeth.

02:40.460 --> 02:41.827
What else have you
got to do?

02:41.829 --> 02:43.162
You're not hooking up
with kate anymore.

02:43.164 --> 02:44.429
No, we're
still friends.

02:44.431 --> 02:45.864
I was thinking of picking up
some chinese

02:45.866 --> 02:48.567
