come to me.

03:01.649 --> 03:03.649
So, roller derby
tonight?

03:03.651 --> 03:05.484
Yeah, no.

03:05.486 --> 03:07.486
All right.

03:07.488 --> 03:09.555
If you change your mind,
meet me there.

03:09.557 --> 03:10.856
