doing here?

03:20.568 --> 03:22.401
Well, I think I'm here
to pick up our daughter,

03:22.403 --> 03:24.536
But if you'd like to keep her,
I'd consider a buyout.

03:24.538 --> 03:26.972
Right, she'll be back
in a minute.

03:26.974 --> 03:28.974
