03:28.976 --> 03:31.810
I have a story to tell you
you're gonna love.

03:31.812 --> 03:34.813
Do you remember that guy
sean I was going out with?

03:34.815 --> 03:37.916
The bozo who told sam
that college was
a waste of time?

03:37.918 --> 03:40.886
Right, that guy.
But you guys had
some fun times, right?

03:40.888 --> 03:44.590
