03:50.965 --> 03:52.898
We're back
together again!

03:52.900 --> 03:55.634
Isn't that crazy?
How crazy is that?

03:55.636 --> 03:56.768
That is-- that--
that is crazy.

03:56.770 --> 03:58.770
You're back together
with a dead guy.

03:58.772 --> 04:00.539
Charlie,
he's different now.

04:00.541 --> 04:02.941
He lost the two ferraris,
the nightclub...

04:02.943 --> 04:04.443
