He's super humble.

04:06.880 --> 04:08.981
You see? You see,
that's how arrogant he is.

04:08.983 --> 04:11.950
He can't just be humble,
he's got to be super humble.

04:11.952 --> 04:13.885
Ah, charlie.

04:13.887 --> 04:16.255
Wasn't expecting
to see you here today.

04:16.257 --> 04:17.789
Oh, my god.
Zombie attack.

04:17.791 --> 04:19.591
Ah.

04:19.593 --> 04:20.892
I don't know
what that means.

04:20.894 --> 04:23.328
It's okay, sean.
Good to see you.

04:23.330 --> 04:25.464
Yeah, hi.
Good to see you also.

04:25.466 --> 04:27.332
- Hey, dad.
- Hey, sam.

04:27.334 --> 04:29.735
So sean's taking sam
to run errands now?

04:29.737 --> 04:32.004
No, I took him.

04:32.006 --> 04:34.773
- He let me drive.
- You what?

04:34.775 --> 04:38.377
She did so good.
You know who she
reminds me of?

04:38.379 --> 04:40.646
Who's that woman?
The race car driver?

04:40.648 --> 04:44.783
- She did commercials
for the thing she was...
- Yeah, all those.

04:44.785 --> 04:46.351
...Trying to sell, I think.
It was, like, a dana, was it?

04:46.353 --> 04:47.819
I know who you mean.

04:47.821 --> 04:49.521
- No, it's not.
It's like...
- She's pretty.

04:49.523 --> 04:51.290
Danica patrick!

04:53.660 --> 04:54.893
She's very pretty.

04:57.330 --> 04:59.431
I'm gonna go start dinner
'cause that's in the other room.

04:59.433 --> 05:02.467
- And I'll help.
- Please.

05:04.804 --> 05:06.972
That guy took my daughter
on her first driving lesson?

05:06.974 --> 05:09.541
He's going down.
Pick a lamp.

05:09.543 --> 05:12.511
I had no idea sean
was gonna do that.

05:12.513 --> 05:14.346
Please don't make
more of this than it is.

05:14.348 --> 05:16.548
Hey, dad.
Can I stay here tonight?

05:16.550 --> 05:19.518
Sean's gonna
teach me how to make
homemade ravioli.

05:19.520 --> 05:21.553
Sure, sweetie.

05:23.856 --> 05:25.957
Her first ravioli.

05:27.994 --> 05:29.895
Where is my pizza?

05:29.897 --> 05:32.864
Whatever happened to your
"30 minutes or less" policy?

05:32.866 --> 05:35.901
It ended 20 years ago?
Well, screw that noise.

05:37.537 --> 05:39.838
I'm-- I'm sorry.
I'm going through a lot
of stuff right now

05:39.840 --> 05:42.474
With my girlfriend
and my kid.

05:42.476 --> 05:44.076
My ex is dating
a douchebag.

05:44.078 --> 05:45.911
