05:56.956 --> 05:59.791
You're not the pizza.
You're a woman.

05:59.793 --> 06:01.360
Why haven't you
answered your phone?

06:01.362 --> 06:02.828
I've been
trying to call.

06:02.830 --> 06:04.696
I'm juggling
a lot of things
right now.

06:04.698 --> 06:06.798
I'm ordering
a pizza and I'm--

06:06.800 --> 06:08.967
And that's
about it.

06:08.969 --> 06:10.435
So, I talked to jen today

06:10.437 --> 06:12.137
And she told me all about
that sean thing.

06:12.139 --> 06:14.139
That sucks, so I thought
maybe you'd want me

06:14.141 --> 06:16.875
To come over
and hang out with you.

06:16.877 --> 06:18.610
