Why?

06:18.612 --> 06:21.480
'cause I'm your friend
and I was concerned.

06:21.482 --> 06:23.982
My friend?

06:23.984 --> 06:25.117
Come here, buddy.

06:25.119 --> 06:27.586
Hey, charlie.
What are you doing?

06:27.588 --> 06:28.887
Oh, please.

06:28.889 --> 06:30.522
