for a classic booty call.

06:32.593 --> 06:35.127
Don't deny it.
You got here faster
than the pizza.

06:35.129 --> 06:37.028
Okay, this was a bad idea.

06:37.030 --> 06:38.930
Good night, I'll see you
in session tomorrow.

06:38.932 --> 06:41.800
