in bed right now.

06:41.802 --> 06:43.835
'cause isn't that
why you're really here?

06:43.837 --> 06:46.471
No, it isn't.

06:46.473 --> 06:50.409
I'm-- I'm sorry.
I must've misread things.

06:50.411 --> 06:52.611
Or did I?

06:52.613 --> 06:53.945
Good night.

06:57.984 --> 06:59.985
Oh, look.
The pizza guy's here.

06:59.987 --> 07:01.653
