have sex with you

07:01.655 --> 07:03.588
Because
he showed up, too.

07:07.860 --> 07:09.761
Oh, my god.
This is horrible.

07:09.763 --> 07:11.763
I can't believe
I agreed to do this.

07:11.765 --> 07:14.533
I can't believe
you're gonna eat this.

07:14.535 --> 07:16.768
I'm so amazed this is
a soup kitchen.

07:16.770 --> 07:18.003
I always thought
it was a restaurant.

07:18.005 --> 07:21.006
I've eaten here,
like, five times.

07:21.008 --> 07:23.675
It's so sad.
I mean, you look in
these people's eyes

07:23.677 --> 07:28.780
Most of them have
never had bottle service
in the vip room.

07:28.782 --> 07:31.183
Sir, you're on
the wrong side
of the counter.

07:31.185 --> 07:32.918
If you come over here,

07:32.920 --> 07:35.220
You'll get
yourself a hot meal
and some new clothes.

07:35.222 --> 07:38.056
What are you doing,
yankin' my nuts?
I'm not homeless.

07:38.058 --> 07:40.826
He's very proud.
I think you should
hose him down

07:40.828 --> 07:43.695
And don't take no
for an answer.

07:43.697 --> 07:47.232
- Let's go, sir.
- What in the hell makes
you think I'm homeless?

07:47.234 --> 07:50.035
How long have you
been wearing that shirt?

07:50.037 --> 07:52.938
I don't know.
Maybe a week.

07:52.940 --> 07:55.240
I see.

07:55.242 --> 07:58.009
Would you prefer
rice or potatoes?

07:58.011 --> 08:00.145
( sighs )

08:00.147 --> 08:02.747
Ah, the hell with it.
Give me the spuds.

08:03.883 --> 08:06.051
God bless you, sir.

08:08.020 --> 08:10.755
Boy, when you look around,
it really makes you think.

08:10.757 --> 08:13.959
"there but for
the grace of god go I."

08:13.961 --> 08:16.862
( scoffs ) not I.
I chose to save my money

08:16.864 --> 08:19.531
