for ralph lauren.

08:43.690 --> 08:46.258
- You did?
- Crazy world, huh?

08:46.260 --> 08:48.727
Hey, can you make sure
the bread is soft,

08:48.729 --> 08:52.864
I've missed my last
152 dental appointments.

08:56.269 --> 08:58.136
Can a homeless man
get a dessert?

08:58.138 --> 09:00.805
