ice cream, she won't
know the difference.

09:29.870 --> 09:31.736
Thanks.

09:31.738 --> 09:35.907
You know, I could
set you up with one
of her giant friends.

09:35.909 --> 09:38.577
Unless kate came
crawling back to you.

09:38.579 --> 09:40.779
No, I thought she did

09:40.781 --> 09:42.714
And I might have messed up
our friendship.

09:42.716 --> 09:44.149
Well, maybe that's
for the best, man.

09:44.151 --> 09:46.051
That situation
with you and kate
was no good.

09:46.053 --> 09:47.752
