but he's buying.

10:45.979 --> 10:47.879
No, no, you're
doing me a favor,

10:47.881 --> 10:50.215
So I'm taking care
of this one.

10:50.217 --> 10:51.816
Wait a minute.
He's the one who
screwed up.

10:51.818 --> 10:53.251
He should be
paying for the drinks.

10:53.253 --> 10:55.353
Are you telling me
he can't even afford that?

10:55.355 --> 10:57.122
