10:58.425 --> 11:00.792
Yes.

11:03.329 --> 11:05.163
Okay, here's 50.

11:05.165 --> 11:06.831
Wow, diamond jim.

11:06.833 --> 11:08.133
You cash
my alimony check?

11:08.135 --> 11:09.834
