without telling you about
it first, all right?

12:14.901 --> 12:16.167
Thank you.

12:16.169 --> 12:18.837
I'm sorry, you're what?
You're moving in?

12:18.839 --> 12:20.905
Yeah.

12:20.907 --> 12:23.808
